entries.femaleVariant: Totally new, totally nova. Got a choom, says it's been on the street a week.
Yeah, heard. 'Parently it's some Biotechnica boosters. Planned leak.
Right. And we're living in a simulation, too.
Seriously. Some sorta drug for chrome tolerance. Slows down the cyberpsycho in all of us.
So they put it out on the street to see what? The side effects?
Chill, chooms. Can't disappoint the corps. Take some tonight, we'll have a fresh report for 'em in the morning.
